msgid "A nib must have at least three on-curve points."
msgstr "En spets måste ha minst tre punkter på kurvan."

#: fontforge/splinestroke.c:589
msgid "The contour is quadratic; a nib must be a cubic contour."
msgstr "Konturen är kvadratisk; en spets måste vara en kubisk kontur."

#: fontforge/splinestroke.c:591
msgid "The contour is open; a nib must be closed."
msgstr "Konturen är öppen; en spets måste vara stängd."

#: fontforge/splinestroke.c:593
msgid ""
"The selected point is the start of a 'tiny' spline; splines that small may "
"cause inaccurate calculations."
msgstr ""
"Den valda punkten är början på en \"liten\" spline; splines som är så små "
"kan orsaka felaktiga beräkningar."

#: fontforge/splinestroke.c:596
msgid ""
"The selected point starts a spline with one control point; nib splines need "
"a defined slope at both points."
msgstr ""
"Den valda punkten startar en spline med en kontrollpunkt; splines med nibbar"
" behöver en definierad lutning vid båda punkterna."

#: fontforge/splinestroke.c:599
msgid ""
"The selected control point's position violates Rule 1 (see documentation)."
msgstr ""
"Den valda kontrollpunktens position bryter mot regel 1 (se dokumentation)."

#: fontforge/splinestroke.c:602
msgid ""
"The selected control point's position violates Rule 2 (see documentation)."
msgstr ""
"Den valda kontrollpunktens position bryter mot regel 2 (se dokumentation)."

#: fontforge/splinestroke.c:605
msgid ""
"The selected control point's position violates Rule 3 (see documentation)."
