#: fontforgeexe/charinfo.c:4539
msgid ""
"Don't display columns of 0s.\n"
"The OpenType lookup allows for up to 8 kinds\n"
"of data, but almost all kerning lookups will use just one.\n"
"Omitting the others makes the behavior clearer."
msgstr ""
"Visa inte kolumner med 0:or.\n"
"OpenType-lookupen tillåter upp till 8 typer\n"
"av data, men nästan alla kerning lookups kommer att använda bara en.\n"
"Om du utelämnar de andra blir beteendet tydligare."

