"For glyph %.60s you refer to a glyph named %.80s, which is not in the font "
"yet. Was this intentional?"
msgstr ""
"För glyf %.60s hänvisar du till en glyf som heter %.80s, som inte finns i "
"teckensnittet ännu. Var det här avsiktligt?"

#: fontforgeexe/lookupui.c:4259 fontforgeexe/lookupui.c:4264
msgid "Duplicate data"
msgstr "Duplicera data"

